bearing
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:an everted vagina or uterus of a ewe [either just prior to or just after lambing; occ. a ewe with a bearing.]


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
